emacs 22
 
M-x describe-coding-system 查看当前buffer编码
 
M-x revert-buffer-with-coding-system 指定编码恢复当前buffer
 
M-x set-buffer-file-coding-system 指定编码保存当前buffer
 
cp936是gbk
 
cp950是big5
 
utf-8是utf8
 
M-x set-buffer-file-coding-system utf-8-dos
 
C-x C-s这样把\n结尾的换行符变成了\r\n
 
M-x set-buffer-file-coding-system utf-8-unix
 
C-x C-s把\r\n结尾的换行符变成了\n
 
dos是\r\n unix是\n mac是\r
